sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant VLLMPod as vLLM/SGLang Pod
    participant ZMQ as ZMQ Subscriber<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ PUB/SUB
    participant Pool as Sharded Worker Pool<br/>(FNV-1a routing)
    participant Adapter as Engine Adapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as KV Block Index<br/>(In-Memory / Redis)
    participant EPP as llm-d-router (EPP)
    participant Tokenizer as UDS Tokenizer<br/>gRPC over UDS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FSBackend as llmd-fs-backend<br/>(vLLM Plugin)
    participant Storage as Shared Storage<br/>NFS/PVC
    participant Evictor as PVC Evictor

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over VLLMPod,Index: Flow 1: KV-Cache Event Ingestion (Write Path)
        VLLMPod->>ZMQ: BlockStored/BlockRemoved event<br/>ZMQ PUB (plaintext, no auth)
        ZMQ->>Pool: Route by FNV-1a(pod_id)<br/>Go channels (in-process)
        Pool->>Adapter: Parse event payload<br/>msgpack (array or map encoded)
        Adapter-->>Pool: Normalized KVEvent
        Pool->>Index: Store/Remove block mapping<br/>Go interface / Redis protocol
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over EPP,Index: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
        EPP->>Tokenizer: Tokenize prompt<br/>gRPC over UDS (no encryption)
        Tokenizer-->>EPP: Token IDs
        EPP->>EPP: Indexer.ScoreTokens()<br/>In-process Go call
        EPP->>Index: Lookup block residency<br/>Go interface / Redis
        Index-->>EPP: Block locations per pod
        EPP->>EPP: Scorer.Score()<br/>Rank pods by cache hit ratio
        Note right of EPP: Route request to<br/>best-scoring pod
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Tokenizer,HFHub: Flow 3: Tokenization (UDS Sidecar)
        EPP->>Tokenizer: RenderChatCompletion RPC<br/>UDS /tmp/tokenizer/tokenizer-uds.socket
        Note right of Tokenizer: First load only:
        Tokenizer->>HFHub: Download tokenizer files<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
        HFHub-->>Tokenizer: Model tokenizer artifacts
        Tokenizer-->>EPP: Token IDs + metadata<br/>gRPC over UDS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over VLLMPod,Storage: Flow 4: KV-Cache Offloading (GPU ↔ Storage)
        VLLMPod->>FSBackend: Offload KV blocks<br/>Python function call (in-process)
        FSBackend->>Storage: Write blocks via cudaMemcpyBatchAsync<br/>POSIX filesystem (file permissions)
        FSBackend->>ZMQ: Publish storage event (optional)<br/>ZMQ PUSH (plaintext)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Storage,Evictor: Flow 5: PVC Eviction (Disk Management)
        Evictor->>Storage: Crawl and check disk usage<br/>POSIX filesystem
        Note right of Evictor: Trigger at 85% usage<br/>Stop at 70% usage
        Evictor->>Storage: Delete stale cache files<br/>Batch deletion (100 files/batch)
        Evictor->>ZMQ: Publish removal events (optional)<br/>ZMQ PUSH (plaintext)
    end
